<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="arrow-n">arrow <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ærəʊ/    美 /'æroʊ/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>箭；箭头 (符号)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Time flies like an arrow. 
光阴似箭。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Follow the arrows to the X-ray department. 
跟着箭头指示的方向去放射科。</p></div></div>